# Adab deploy rules

- **Deploy repo:** `adab-real-estate-web` only — not `adab-ng-site`
- **Production:** https://adab.ng via Vercel scope `adab-techs-projects`
- **Branch:** `master` is production
- Run `npm run build` before every deploy; fix all errors
- Never commit `.env.local` or API keys
- Add new env vars to `.env.example` with comments
- Deploy command: `npx vercel deploy --prod --yes --scope adab-techs-projects`
- Do not re-add Zoho CRM integration

## Pre-deploy checklist

1. Build passes locally
2. Env vars set in Vercel dashboard (see `.env.example`)
3. Supabase redirect URLs include `https://adab.ng/auth/callback`
4. Commit message describes user-facing change, not file list
